"manages your schedule and appointments."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Kalenderappen</font></strong> "
"administrerer din kalender og dine aftaler."

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Timesheet App</font></strong> "
"tracks billable hours and time spent."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Tidsregistreringsappen</font></"
"strong> registrerer fakturerbare timer og tidsforbrug."

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Sign App offers <strong>three levels of signatures</strong>, allowing "
"you to choose the appropriate level based on the document’s importance and "
"legal requirements."
msgstr ""
"E-Signaturappen tilbyder <strong>tre underskriftsniveauer</strong>, så du "
"kan vælge det, der passer til dokumentets betydning og juridiske krav."

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
