"the required <strong>Know Your Customer (KYC) assessment</strong> before "
"accepting a case."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong>CRM-appen</strong> til at administrere kundeinteraktioner og "
"foretage den nødvendige <strong>Know Your Customer-vurdering (KYC)</strong>, "
"inden du accepterer en sag."

