"Use the <strong>Sign App</strong> to request a signature from the partner to"
" approve the completed legal documents before delivery and invoicing the "
"client."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong>e-Signaturappen</strong> til at anmode om en underskrift fra "
"partneren for at godkende de færdige juridiske dokumenter, inden de leveres "
"og faktureres til kunden."

